cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.MM 

The paper deals with improving the visual explanations of deep convolutional networks, which is a problem in computer vision. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a generalized method for explainable deep learning, which falls under the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also evaluates the proposed method on image caption generation, which falls under the sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language). Finally, the paper evaluates the proposed method on 3D action recognition, which falls under the sub-category of cs.MM (Multimedia).
